:"信有因果報應<br />\n人地幾醜惡都係人地嘅事 <br />\n佢地受得起個報應咪得囉<br />\n自己做返好自己就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20ca59b14c7c7cfe1f0801a85ed5ae1c3340e4b","tid":151903,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係人性醜惡，想探究吓唔同人嘅本質如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起都興奮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人太醜陋<br />\n曾經好想將來做呢類既野<br />\n但怕接受唔到人性既醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申成日感受到人既自私自利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得厭惡既同時亦努力嘗試相信世界仍然有美麗既一面 總有d人愛既人<br />\n但我最撚憎d疑似樂於助人既人成日周圍同人講自己幾大愛 成日做義工etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係由心幫人既話根本唔需要人地認同自己既付出<br />\n周圍同人講博人地好感只令人反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係咁不滿付出冇回報一開始就咪撚付出<br />\n唔好付出完係度叫春話自己成日做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野對人好但得唔到回報呢d天方夜譚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b6c7b40dab1c8f36565a14779a1f1751b705c5","tid":151903,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信有因果報應<br />\n人地幾醜惡都係人地嘅事 <br />\n佢地受得起個報應咪得囉<br />\n自己做返好自己就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger 如果接觸d仆街既話唯有盡量疏遠<br />\nD仆街咁賤咁撚自私咁撚鍾意玩攻心計係佢地既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb581ab2773360f9813a05749b00cbac2a1918e5","tid":151903,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"屌見到有咁多呢種諗法既人好熱血！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\